0:00:00.840,0:00:04.900
Ndingautaura newe here, hama?

0:00:04.900,0:00:07.800
Mai vako varipi?

0:00:07.800,0:00:09.580
Chengeta mai vako.

0:00:09.580,0:00:10.200
Handiti?

0:00:10.200,0:00:10.960
Handiti?

0:00:10.960,0:00:13.100
Chengeta mai vako.

0:00:13.100,0:00:14.040
Ndinokutendai, changamire.

0:00:14.040,0:00:15.780
Mai vako mudzimai akanaka.

0:00:15.780,0:00:16.500
Ndinokutendai, changamire.

0:00:16.500,0:00:20.020
Handizivi kuti sei vachivadana zvese (marudzi ese) emazita.

0:00:20.020,0:00:22.860
Vanovati muroyi. Hapana chavasina kumudana mukadzi uyu.

0:00:22.860,0:00:24.140
Hongu, changamire.

0:00:24.140,0:00:25.320
Ndinokutendai, Jesu!

0:00:25.320,0:00:27.880
Sei imi vanhu muchidavira kuti mukadzi uyu muroyi?

0:00:27.880,0:00:32.120
Ndizvo zvavari kudanwa ne vanhu.

0:00:32.120,0:00:35.940
Kunyangwe mhuri yababa vangu, vose vanovati muroyi.

0:00:35.940,0:00:40.540
Ndiyo mhuri yangu kudivi rababa vangu vanoti amai vangu muroyi.

0:00:40.540,0:00:47.740
Iri ndiro dambudziko ramunaro, kudana munhu asina mhosva - 'chisikwa cha Mwari' -

0:00:47.740,0:00:49.600
munhu asiri muroyi momuti muroyi.

0:00:49.600,0:00:52.760
Uyu mukadzi akachema zve kuchema.

0:00:52.760,0:00:54.320
Chaizvo, changamire.

0:00:54.320,0:00:59.720
Hapana mumwe wenyu achabudirira kunze kwekuti mudzimai uyu agamuchira rukumbiro rwe ruregero

0:00:59.720,0:01:03.460
nekunge Mweya wa Mwari wakukanganwira iwe.

0:01:03.460,0:01:05.780
Uyu mukadzi akatambura.

0:01:05.780,0:01:08.040
Uchauya ne mukadzi uyu pano.

0:01:08.040,0:01:09.620
Handiti? Endai munondimirira.

0:01:09.620,0:01:10.680
Ndinokutendai, changamire.

0:01:11.220,0:01:12.560
Hazvisi iwewe chete.

0:01:12.560,0:01:16.660
Tichakumbira amai ne Mweya wa Mwari uye ivo vachabvuma.

0:01:16.660,0:01:18.660
Mhuri yose ichasunungurwa.

0:01:18.660,0:01:22.960
Vakatuka mukadzi uyu.

0:01:22.960,0:01:26.300
Nemhaka yaizvozvo, ari kugara kuseri kwemba.

0:01:26.300,0:01:27.240
Hongu, changamire.

0:01:28.200,0:01:33.680
Zita rangu ndi Charles Benson.

0:01:33.680,0:01:35.320
Ini ndinobva ku Delta State.

0:01:35.320,0:01:45.140
Mukadzi akamira pedyo neni ndi amai vangu avo ini pachangu ne mhuri takavati muroyi.

0:01:45.140,0:01:49.480
Vanhu ava vari shure kwangu ndivo vakoma nehanzvadzi dzangu.

0:01:49.480,0:01:56.620
Ava mai vari pano ndi ambuya vangu.

0:01:56.620,0:02:02.720
Svondo yapfuura, patakanga tiri musvondo yekutanga, munhu wa Mwari akandidana.

0:02:02.720,0:02:05.300
Akandibvunza kuti amai vangu vaiva kupi.

0:02:05.300,0:02:08.060
Ndakati amai vangu vaiva kumba.

0:02:08.060,0:02:12.020
Akabva ataura kuti ndinofanira kuvachengeta.

0:02:12.020,0:02:13.900
Ndakati, "Zvakanaka, changamire".

0:02:13.900,0:02:16.740
Mushure mezvo, akaprofita kwandiri.

0:02:16.740,0:02:19.520
Akabvunza, "Sei vachidana amai vako mazita ose ose?"

0:02:19.520,0:02:25.800
"Vanovati muroyi, haasi muroyi, haana mhosva."

0:02:25.800,0:02:28.100
Akataura kuti kunyange ini ndinovati muroyi.

0:02:28.100,0:02:31.980
Akati nekuda kwe izvozvo, vakachema.

0:02:31.980,0:02:36.900
Nemhaka yekuchema kwake, hapana anobudirira mumhuri.

0:02:36.900,0:02:40.420
Saka, akati ini ndinofanira kuvaunza pano.

0:02:40.420,0:02:44.100
Ndokusaka ndavaunza pano nemhuri yangu.

0:02:44.100,0:02:47.180
Zvakarehwa nemunhu wa Mwari zvaive zvechokwadi.

0:02:47.180,0:02:51.060
Takavati muroyi ndokuvaisa kuseri kwemba.

0:02:51.060,0:02:54.460
Zita rangu ndi Fatima.

0:02:54.460,0:03:01.920
Apo murume wangu akafa, mhuri yakandidana kumusangano wavo.

0:03:01.920,0:03:05.020
Vakandibvunza kuti chii chakaitika.

0:03:05.020,0:03:09.340
Ndakavaudza kuti ndakanga ndisingazivi chakauraya hama yavo.

0:03:09.340,0:03:13.620
Ivo vakati ini ndini ndakauraya murume wangu.

0:03:13.620,0:03:16.480
Ndakati ndakanga ndisingazivi chinhu pamusoro pazvo,

0:03:16.480,0:03:18.480
kuti akanga achirwara.

0:03:18.480,0:03:21.540
Mushure mekunge tabva kumusha,

0:03:21.540,0:03:25.080
imba iyo vana vangu, murume wangu neni taigara,

0:03:25.080,0:03:29.120
Mhuri yemurume wangu yakandidzinga kunze.

0:03:29.120,0:03:34.580
Ndakakumbira kuti vaifanira kundirega ini nevana vangu tigare.

0:03:34.580,0:03:38.760
Vakataura kuti vakanga vatogovera imba uye vakaipa kune mumwe munhu.

0:03:38.760,0:03:43.200
Vakakanda midziyo yangu kunze ndokubva vakandidzinga.

0:03:43.200,0:03:47.400
Ndakanga ndisina pokugara uye kunyange kudya kwaive kwakaoma.

0:03:47.400,0:03:52.600
Ava mai vakandiona ndichitambudzika apo midziyo yangu yakanga iri panze.

0:03:52.600,0:03:56.880
Vakasangana neni uye vakati havaigona kundisiya ndakadaro.

0:03:56.880,0:04:02.140
Vakatora imwe midziyo ndokuenda nayo kuseri kwavaimboshanda.

0:04:02.140,0:04:06.460
Kwakanga kuri kuseri, neche kunze

0:04:06.460,0:04:10.180
Vakandipa mari yekugara ne kubika.

0:04:10.180,0:04:13.640
Isu tinonyatsonzwisisa zvakaitika kwamuri - marwadzo acho.

0:04:13.640,0:04:16.140
Ndicho chikonzero nei takukokai pano nhasi

0:04:16.140,0:04:18.760
kuti nyika izive kuti hamusi muroyi

0:04:18.760,0:04:23.160
uye kuti tine urombo zvikuru pane zvakaitika.

0:04:23.160,0:04:27.480
Iri ndiro zuva rakanaka kune umwe neumwe wedu.

0:04:27.480,0:04:32.360
Tine urombo kwazvo; amai havasi muroyi.

0:04:32.360,0:04:38.380
Mwanakomana, tapota pfugama nemabvi ako umbundire mai vako.

0:04:48.580,0:04:53.040
Saka, tapota, amai, vanyengetererei.

0:04:53.040,0:04:55.400
Amai vanamatirei.

0:04:55.400,0:05:05.100
Saka, tapota, sezvamuri kupa munyengetero uyu, Ishe waMasimba Ose ari kunyengetererawo ivo.

0:05:05.100,0:05:06.780
Vari kutsvaga kubudirira

0:05:06.780,0:05:11.680
uye havazivi chivi chavakaita, nekusaziva.

0:05:11.680,0:05:14.280
Zvino, amai vakukanganwirai.

0:05:14.280,0:05:16.560
Amai, munofanira kukanganwira munhu wose.

0:05:16.560,0:05:19.080
Vose ava imhuri yemurume wangu.

0:05:19.080,0:05:21.980
Mwanakomana wokupedzisira akakanda zvinhu zvangu panze.

0:05:21.980,0:05:23.980
Saka, iwe wakarasa zvinhu zvaamai?

0:05:23.980,0:05:25.860
Yakanga iri nokuda kwemvumo kubva kumba, changamire.

0:05:25.860,0:05:28.500
Anoda munyengetero.

0:05:28.500,0:05:31.440
Anoda munyengetero nokuti akanga asingazivi zvaaita.

0:05:31.440,0:05:33.440
Akarasa zvinhu zvangu zvose kure.

0:05:33.440,0:05:34.800
Ndiye akarasa midziyo yenyu yose?

0:05:34.800,0:05:35.580
Hongu.

0:05:35.580,0:05:38.600
Ndiwo waiva murayiro kubva kumba.

0:05:38.600,0:05:40.880
Ndicho chikonzero nei mai vakati iwe unoda munyengetero.

0:05:40.880,0:05:43.500
Amai vanoziva kuti iwe wakaita mukusaziva.

0:06:10.020,0:06:12.220
Vati ivo vakadzinga mukadzi uyu panze.

0:06:12.220,0:06:13.400
Ndivo vakanga vachivatarisira.

0:06:13.400,0:06:15.740
Hapana kubva kumhuri akabvunza pamusoro pake kana vana,

0:06:15.740,0:06:18.020
kuti vaive vachidyei kana kuti vaiva sei.

0:06:18.020,0:06:20.740
Saka, zvapera zvino. Tinotenda Mwari.

0:06:20.740,0:06:23.620
Mwari ndiye akatipa chizaruriro ichi

0:06:23.620,0:06:27.480
uye Mwari mumwe chete ari kuti, "Zvapera".

0:06:27.480,0:06:34.600
Munhu wa Mwari, ndinokanganwira vanhu vose vakaita kuti nditambure.

0:06:34.600,0:06:50.600
Mhuri Yakabatanidzwa Muzita ra Jesu

0:06:50.600,0:06:56.640
Tinovimba kuti wakurudzirwa nevhidhiyo yawabva mukuona.

0:06:56.640,0:07:02.980
Tinya apa kuti unyorese kupupurira zvakawanda pamusoro pesimba ra Mwari pabasa munguva yatiri nhasi

0:07:02.980,0:07:07.280
kuti ugare uri pamusoro pezvichagoburwa zvehuporofita,dzikinuro,

0:07:07.280,0:07:12.240
mharidzo nezvapupu zvinobva ku Synagogue Church of All Nations

